center Melinda Harrison's 12.9, plus 9.6 rebounds, which leads the WCC. USF is 
the WCC's best three-point shooting team, hitting 45.7% in conference games. 
Alice Solis leads the WCC in three-point percentage at 46.9%, and Boyenga is 
second at 46.7%. ALAN DROOZ 
