AFRICA; UNITED STATES -- TRADE -- SOUTH AFRICA; RACIAL RELATIONS -- SOUTH 
AFRICA; BLACKS -- SOUTH AFRICA; SOUTH AFRICA -- GOVERNMENT; GOVERNMENT REFORM; 
APARTHEID 
</P>
