ETHNIC GROUPS; ARMENIANS; USSR -- ARMED FORCES; GORBACHEV, MIKHAIL S; DOMESTIC 
POLICY; NATIONALISM; USSR -- MARTIAL LAW; PEACE MOVEMENTS 
</P>
